be 欣賞吓條片嘅高清版本：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pFt8kmtpoV4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpFt8kmtpoV4&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfrwuBxQMtbc6xR8MkqxZcasw%3D&h=93e3ebff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pFt8kmtpoV4</a>"},{"pid":"1496d906c4a56e7749a317d282367628cd50b814","tid":1939766,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5713f2c2aee19e43815656b35b1c767108c0143e","tid":1939766,"uid":192034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62c0f1ef89cbe2ff1806e926e096a2c4d1edca5b","tid":1939766,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bc72001f6d4066af1ee50eb59c9541ff167b36f","tid":1939766,"uid":192034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T13:45:04.000Z","msg":"全球都要反思依點啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D8yu2Q5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD8yu2Q5.png&h=dfd8e593&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T14:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾時賣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T14:41:21.000Z","msg":"兩至三星期後，每個國家都要反思番自己嘅工業，特別係香港，其次就要發展番自己嘅農業，唔駛比人揸住春袋，記得定期買下本地菜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n㊙【先睹為快🔥口罩機開箱】🔥<br />\n<br />\n來自美國及台灣防菌Filter？Ready✅<br />\n有認證無塵車間？Ready✅<br />\n口罩機？Ready✅‼️‼️‼️<br />\n<br />\n皇天不負有心人😘等咗足足一月，口罩機終於由台灣送到嚟將軍澳總部！（R小隊鬆一口氣💨）聽到口罩機到埗開始組裝，小編差啲連個心💓都跳埋出嚟，裝完之後仲要做一啲調整及試產&hellip; 唔好講咁多，去片！<br />\n<br />\n雖然等港產口罩等到花兒也謝了🥀不過唔使咁快攞銀包，因為口罩一定要做足功夫，質素同可靠嘅生產設備最緊要，否則戴咗等於無戴！所以必須要做到防菌防病毒🦠嘅合規格口罩😷<br />\n<br 